    <string name="help_title">App Functionality</string>
    <string name="help_content">
        &lt;b&gt;Eyes-Free Monitoring&lt;/b&gt;: Stay alert through distinct auditory patterns representing distance and severity, designed for situational awareness while driving or active.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &lt;b&gt;Country-Wide Scope&lt;/b&gt;: Monitor the broader picture of alerts across the entire country in real-time.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &lt;b&gt;Sound Legend&lt;/b&gt;:&lt;br/&gt;
        • &lt;b&gt;Urgent&lt;/b&gt;: A staccato sequence of tones shifting in pitch. It starts with high-pitched chirps for distant alerts and transitions into deep, low-pitched tones for threats near you.&lt;br/&gt;
        • &lt;b&gt;Caution&lt;/b&gt;: A steady, alternating two-note melody alerting to activity in neighboring areas.&lt;br/&gt;
        • &lt;b&gt;All Clear&lt;/b&gt;: A soft, ascending three-note melody.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &lt;b&gt;Disclaimer&lt;/b&gt;: This is an unofficial tool. Always prioritize official instructions and sirens from the Home Front Command.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &lt;b&gt;Internal Alpha&lt;/b&gt;: You are using a development version for testing purposes. Please report any issues.
    </string>
